headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Trane Technologies (TT) After Strong Multi‑Year Share Price Gains?

headline: TT Q4 Deep Dive: Commercial HVAC and Data Center Demand Drive Results, Backlog Hits High
summary: HVAC company Trane (NYSE:TT) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q4 CY2025, with sales up 5.5% year on year to $5.14 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.86 per share was 1.6% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
